name: MegaLong (3X) 20+ Year US Treasury Daily Leveraged Alternative ETF
longDescription: In order to achieve its investment objective, each Triple Levered ETF may invest all or a portion of its portfolio in interest bearing accounts, T-Bills and/or other financial instruments, including derivatives such as futures contracts, options on futures contracts, forward contracts, swap agreements, options on securities and indices, or any combination of the foregoing. The fund seeks daily investment results, before fees, expenses, and other transaction costs, that endeavour to correspond to three times (3X) the daily performance of its underlying benchmark.
